text: Mozo is a Spanish surname. Notable people with the name include: * Alan Mozo (born 1997), Mexican association football player * Alejandro Gutiérrez Mozo (born 1995), Spanish association football player * Belén Mozo (born 1988), Spanish professional golfer * Nicolás de Vergara el Mozo (1540–1606), Spanish sculptor, architect, ironworker and glazier ==See also== * Mozo (disambiguation)
